## Comandos para gerar JWT Secret:

### Linux/Mac:
# openssl rand -base64 32

### Windows (PowerShell):
# -join ((65..90) + (97..122) + (48..57) | Get-Random -Count 32 | % {[char]$_})

### Node.js:
# node -e "console.log(require('crypto').randomBytes(32).toString('hex'))"